  "remarks": "KPi.023. President of Tanchon Commercial Bank. Passport no: 290320764 (issued by the Democratic People's Republic of Korea). Kim Tong My’ong is the President of Tanchon Commercial Bank and has held various positions within Tanchon Commercial bank since at least 2002. He has also played a role in managing Amroggang’s affairs.; Listing: First listed on 2/03/2016 (amended on 26/07/2022)",
